{"id":6718,"date":"2024-01-23T16:08:05","date_gmt":"2024-01-23T16:08:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bake250.isdeveloping.com\/gentlecan\/?page_id=6718"},"modified":"2024-07-08T13:37:24","modified_gmt":"2024-07-08T13:37:24","slug":"politica-de-cookies","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/gentlecan.es\/politica-de-cookies\/","title":{"rendered":"Pol\u00edtica de Cookies"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"6718\" class=\"elementor elementor-6718\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-22d3eec elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"22d3eec\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3e33996\" data-id=\"3e33996\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac0c151 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ac0c151\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pol\u00edtica de Cookies\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab41840 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ab41840\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">1. Introducci\u00f3n<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Nuestra web,\u00a0<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #00544d; text-decoration-line: underline; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s;\" href=\"https:\/\/gentlecan.es\/\">https:\/\/gentlecan.es<\/a>\u00a0(en adelante: \u00abla web\u00bb) utiliza cookies y otras tecnolog\u00edas relacionadas (para mayor comodidad, todas las tecnolog\u00edas se denominan \u00abcookies\u00bb). Las cookies tambi\u00e9n son colocadas por terceros a los que hemos contratado. En el siguiente documento te informamos sobre el uso de cookies en nuestra web.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">2. \u00bfQu\u00e9 son las cookies?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Una cookie es un peque\u00f1o archivo que se env\u00eda junto con las p\u00e1ginas de esta web y que tu navegador almacena en el disco duro de su ordenador u otro dispositivo. La informaci\u00f3n almacenada puede ser devuelta a nuestros servidores o a los servidores de terceros apropiados durante una visita posterior.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">3. \u00bfQu\u00e9 son los scripts?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Un script es un fragmento de c\u00f3digo de programa que se utiliza para hacer que nuestra web funcione correctamente y de forma interactiva. Este c\u00f3digo se ejecuta en nuestro servidor o en tu dispositivo.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">4. \u00bfQu\u00e9 es una baliza web?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Una baliza web (o una etiqueta de p\u00edxel) es una peque\u00f1a e invisible pieza de texto o imagen en una web que se utiliza para monitorear el tr\u00e1fico en una web. Para ello, se almacenan varios datos sobre usted mediante estas balizas web.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">5. Cookies<\/h2>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.1 Cookies t\u00e9cnicas o funcionales<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Algunas cookies aseguran que ciertas partes de la web funcionen correctamente y que tus preferencias de usuario sigan record\u00e1ndose. Al colocar cookies funcionales, te facilitamos la visita a nuestra web. De esta manera, no necesitas introducir repetidamente la misma informaci\u00f3n cuando visitas nuestra web y, por ejemplo, los art\u00edculos permanecen en tu cesta de la compra hasta que hayas pagado. Podemos colocar estas cookies sin tu consentimiento.<\/p>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.2 Cookies de estad\u00edsticas<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Utilizamos cookies estad\u00edsticas para optimizar la experiencia de la web para nuestros usuarios. Con estas cookies estad\u00edsticas obtenemos informaci\u00f3n sobre el uso de nuestra web.\u00a0Te pedimos tu permiso para colocar cookies de estad\u00edsticas.<\/p>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.3 Cookies publicitarias<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">En esta web usamos cookies de publicidad, permiti\u00e9ndonos obtener informaci\u00f3n sobre los resultados de la campa\u00f1a. Esto sucede en base a un perfil que creamos basado en tu comportamiento en\u00a0<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #00544d; text-decoration-line: underline; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s;\" href=\"https:\/\/gentlecan.es\/\">https:\/\/gentlecan.es<\/a>. Con estas cookies t\u00fa, como visitante de la web, est\u00e1s asociado a un ID \u00fanico, pero estas cookies no crear\u00e1n un perfil de tu comportamiento e intereses para presentarte anuncios personalizados.<\/p>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.4 Cookies de marketing\/seguimiento<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Las cookies de marketing\/seguimiento son cookies, o cualquier otra forma de almacenamiento local, usadas para crear perfiles de usuario para mostrar publicidad o para hacer el seguimiento del usuario en esta web o en varias webs con fines de marketing similares.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Debido a que estas cookies est\u00e1n marcadas como cookies de seguimiento, te pedimos tu permiso para colocarlas.<\/p>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.5 Redes sociales<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">En nuestra web hemos incluido contenido de Instagram para promover p\u00e1ginas web (p.ej.: \u00abMe gusta\u00bb, \u00abPinear\u00bb) o compartir (p.ej.: \u00abtuitear\u00bb) en redes sociales como Instagram. Este contenido est\u00e1 incrustado con c\u00f3digo derivado de Instagram y guarda cookies. Este contenido podr\u00eda procesar cierta informaci\u00f3n para anuncios personalizados.<\/p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Por favor lea la pol\u00edtica de privacidad de estas redes sociales (que puede cambiar frecuentemente) para saber que hacen con sus datos (personales) que procesan usando estas cookies. Los datos que reciben son anonimizados lo m\u00e1ximo posible. Instagram est\u00e1 ubicado en los Estados Unidos.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 22px; line-height: 65px; font-family: tiempos-headline; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #444444; letter-spacing: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-color: #ffffff;\">6. Cookies usadas<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ce2e60 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"7ce2e60\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class= \"cky-audit-table-element\"><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0711acc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0711acc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-family: tiempos-headline; font-weight: bold; line-height: 65px; color: #444444; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">7. Consentimiento<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Cuando visites nuestra web por primera vez, te mostraremos una ventana emergente con una explicaci\u00f3n sobre las cookies. Tan pronto como hagas clic en \u00abGuardar preferencias\u00bb, aceptas que usemos las categor\u00edas de cookies y plugins que has seleccionado en la ventana emergente, tal y como se describe en esta pol\u00edtica de cookies. Puedes desactivar el uso de cookies a trav\u00e9s de tu navegador, pero, por favor, ten en cuenta que nuestra web puede dejar de funcionar correctamente.<\/p>\n<p class=\"cmplz-subtitle\" style=\"margin: 25px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">7.1 Gestiona tus ajustes de consentimiento<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-family: tiempos-headline; font-weight: bold; line-height: 65px; color: #444444; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">8. Activaci\u00f3n\/desactivaci\u00f3n y borrado de cookies<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Puedes utilizar tu navegador de Internet para eliminar las cookies de forma autom\u00e1tica o manual. Tambi\u00e9n puedes especificar que ciertas cookies no pueden ser colocadas. Otra opci\u00f3n es cambiar los ajustes de tu navegador de Internet para que recibas un mensaje cada vez que se coloca una cookie. Para obtener m\u00e1s informaci\u00f3n sobre estas opciones, consulta las instrucciones de la secci\u00f3n \u00abAyuda\u00bb de tu navegador.<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Ten en cuenta que nuestra web puede no funcionar correctamente si todas las cookies est\u00e1n desactivadas. Si borras las cookies de tu navegador, se volver\u00e1n a colocar despu\u00e9s de tu consentimiento cuando vuelvas a visitar nuestras webs.<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-family: tiempos-headline; font-weight: bold; line-height: 65px; color: #444444; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">9. Tus derechos con respecto a los datos personales<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Tienes los siguientes derechos con respecto a tus datos personales:<\/p>\n\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px 0px 15px 15px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Tiene derecho a saber por qu\u00e9 se necesitan tus datos personales, qu\u00e9 suceder\u00e1 con ellos y durante cu\u00e1nto tiempo se conservar\u00e1n.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Derecho de acceso: tienes derecho a acceder a tus datos personales que conocemos.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Derecho de rectificaci\u00f3n: tienes derecho a completar, rectificar, borrar o bloquear tus datos personales cuando lo desees.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Si nos das tu consentimiento para procesar tus datos, tienes derecho a revocar dicho consentimiento y a que se eliminen tus datos personales.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Derecho de cesi\u00f3n de tus datos: tienes derecho a solicitar todos tus datos personales al responsable del tratamiento y a transferirlos \u00edntegramente a otro responsable del tratamiento.<\/li>\n \t<li style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; list-style: outside disc;\">Derecho de oposici\u00f3n: puedes oponerte al tratamiento de tus datos. Nosotros cumplimos con esto, a menos que existan motivos justificados para el procesamiento.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Para ejercer estos derechos, por favor, contacta con nosotros. Por favor, consulta los detalles de contacto en la parte inferior de esta pol\u00edtica de cookies. Si tienes alguna queja sobre c\u00f3mo gestionamos tus datos, nos gustar\u00eda que nos la hicieras saber, pero tambi\u00e9n tienes derecho a enviar una queja a la autoridad supervisora (la autoridad de protecci\u00f3n de datos).<\/p>\n\n<h2 style=\"font-family: tiempos-headline; font-weight: bold; line-height: 65px; color: #444444; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0px; margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">10. Datos de contacto<\/h2>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Para preguntas y\/o comentarios sobre nuestra pol\u00edtica de cookies y esta declaraci\u00f3n, por favor, contacta con nosotros usando los siguientes datos de contacto:<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #676767; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span class=\"cmplz-contact-organisation\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Arellis Maltez Gutierrez<\/span>\n<span class=\"cmplz-contact-address\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Avda. Men\u00e9ndez Pelayo 19, Bajo local 6, 28009 Madrid<\/span>\n<span class=\"cmplz-contact-country\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Espa\u00f1a<\/span>\nWeb:\u00a0<span class=\"cmplz-contact-domain\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: #00544d; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s;\" href=\"https:\/\/gentlecan.es\/\">https:\/\/gentlecan.es<\/a><\/span>\nCorreo electr\u00f3nico:\u00a0<span class=\"cmplz-contact-email\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span class=\"cmplz-obfuscate\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: bidi-override; text-wra